description:
Thanks to Universal Pictures for Sponsoring this Video!
Can a stuntman become a HERO? Find out in The Fall Guy! Watch in Theaters on May 3.
 
In Universal’s new movie ‘The Fall Guy’, Ryan Gosling plays a stuntman turned savior when he has to go rescue the movie star he’s doubling. But does a stunt double have the necessary skills to ACTUALLY pull off a rescue mission?
